&lt;li&gt;Enable system-level diagnostics, logging, and secure boot configuration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Automate setup, flashing, health checks, and test execution on target hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
