&lt;p&gt;Wayve is looking for an experienced, senior public policy leader to build and execute our Japan public policy strategy. This role will lead all public policy outreach and execution across Japan — shaping regulatory pathways, securing relationships with national &amp;amp; local stakeholders, and ensuring Wayve’s product, safety and commercial strategies are aligned with the Japanese regulatory and political environment. You will be Wayve’s most senior public policy representative in Japan, responsible for delivering tangible regulatory and commercial outcomes that enable testing and deployment of AV2.0.&lt;/p&gt;
