&lt;li&gt;Ensure product roadmaps and trial programs meet Japanese regulatory requirements and anticipate likely regulatory changes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor Japanese policy, legislative and regulatory developments; provide timely analysis, scenario planning and recommendations to senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support senior leadership and spokespeople for public appearances and press engagements as required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver measurable policy outcomes (e.g., approvals, pilot permits, regulatory clarifications), and define KPIs to track progress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage budgets, external consultants, contractors and local legal advisors as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
