&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with creating and executing safety management activities, spanning safety policy, assurance, risk management and safety promotion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applied experience with safety in a fleet operations environment or similar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner and stakeholder engagement experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Risk management tools and evaluation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-functional project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Desirable&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Safety management system experience in an automotive, aerospace or transportation setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operations or safety experience with platform marketplace businesses, such as ride-sharing, delivery, micromobility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with global autonomous vehicle test and deployment regulations and reporting requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
