&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Build and operate monitoring, logging, alerting, and on-call tooling that enables fast detection, diagnosis, and recovery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
