&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a Staff ML Performance Engineer to join our Training Tech team working on optimizing large scale ML jobs to enable scaling our models to the next order of magnitude. A successful candidate will increase efficiency of training and inference workloads in order to allow Wayve to train larger models faster.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Key responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
