&lt;p&gt;Wayve is building the AI Driver to power autonomous mobility at global scale. As we deploy robotaxi services with leading partners, we are hiring a Strategic Partnerships Manager to help scale our commercial ecosystem in London and Tokyo. This is a high-impact role at the intersection of autonomy, mobility platforms, and automotive OEMs — focused on enabling safe, scalable L4 deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead day-to-day commercial execution of Wayve’s robotaxi partnerships in your market, working closely with ride-hailing platforms, OEM partners and cross-functional internal teams to deliver successful pilot launches and fleet scale-up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role combines strategic thinking with hands-on execution across product readiness, operational launch, and commercial scaling.&lt;/p&gt;
